	ay\, Sept 19\, 8 p.m.\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Sunday\, Sept 20\
	, 2 p.m. \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Sunday\, Sept 20\, 7:30 p.m. 
	\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Tuesday\, Sept 22\, 7:30 p.m. \n			\n	
